OL,3,CUK to hit 30C this weekend - but why
OL,4,Cis it different to May's heatwave?
OL,6,FAfter a much cooler and fresher start
OL,7,Fto June, it's all change by the end of
OL,8,Fthe week.
OL,10,FThis weekend the summery weather
OL,11,Freturns, with temperatures likely to
OL,12,Frise beyond 30C across some south and
OL,13,Fsouth-eastern locations.
OL,15,FBut it's likely to feel a little
OL,16,Fdifferent to the record-breaking
OL,17,Ftemperatures we saw in May, as this
OL,18,Fheat brings higher humidity.
OL,20,FHere's how this week is shaping up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
