OL,3,CUK to hit 30C this weekend - but why
OL,4,Cis it different to May's heatwave?
OL,6,FWhy is the weather improving?
OL,8,FAfter two weeks of low pressure
OL,9,Fsystems rolling in from the Atlantic,
OL,10,Fhigh pressure starts to take over from
OL,11,Fthe south by the end of the week.
OL,13,FSo far, June has had a cooler, fresher
OL,14,Fand rainy theme, but we can expect a
OL,15,Fvery different feel this weekend.
OL,17,FInitially the warm weather will come
OL,18,Fto southern countries of England and
OL,19,FWales, before other areas of the UK
OL,20,Fwill see an improvement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
