OL,3,CUK to hit 30C this weekend - but why
OL,4,Cis it different to May's heatwave?
OL,6,FWhat temperatures can we expect?
OL,8,FIt will start to feel warmer for many
OL,9,Fof us by the tail end of the week.
OL,11,FAs the recent weather settles down, it
OL,12,Fwill become drier with more sunshine
OL,13,Fand temperatures will be boosted to
OL,14,Fthose you would expect for June.
OL,16,FIt's likely to get to close to 26-27C
OL,17,Fby Friday, 28C on Saturday with
OL,18,Ftemperatures peaking around 29-30C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
