OL,3,CUK to hit 30C this weekend - but why
OL,4,Cis it different to May's heatwave?
OL,6,FInto next week, temperatures will
OL,7,Flikely to rise beyond 30C across some
OL,8,Fsouth and south-eastern locations.
OL,10,FHow will these temperatures feel
OL,11,Fdifferent to the heatwave in May?
OL,13,FThis heat will be influenced by warmer
OL,14,Fair from the continent - as the high
OL,15,Fpressure establishes itself from the
OL,16,Fsouth.
