OL,3,CUK to hit 30C this weekend - but why
OL,4,Cis it different to May's heatwave?
OL,6,FWith this comes a higher humidity - we
OL,7,Fcan expect a more humid or muggy feel
OL,8,Fwith the higher temperatures into
OL,9,FSaturday, the rest of the weekend and
OL,10,Finto the new week.
OL,12,FOvernight temperatures will be higher
OL,13,Ftoo, so there will be the addition of
OL,14,Fmilder - and in places warm and stuffy
OL,15,F- nights.
OL,17,FMuch of northern England, Scotland and
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland will escape the humid
OL,19,For muggy air and feel a lot more
OL,20,Fcomfortable - both by day and by night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
